🌐 Computer Networks (Mock Interview Round)
🎤 Q1: What happens when you type google.com?
Expected Answer (Structured)
DNS resolves domain → IP
TCP 3-way handshake
TLS handshake (if HTTPS)
HTTP GET request
Routing through routers
Server response
Browser renders page

👉 Tip: Always answer in steps

🎤 Q2: TCP vs UDP – which will you choose?
Smart Answer

“Depends on use case”

TCP → reliability needed (banking)
UDP → speed needed (gaming/streaming)

👉 Shows decision-making ability

🎤 Q3: What is subnetting and why needed?
Perfect Answer

Subnetting divides a network into smaller networks to:

improve performance
enhance security
reduce congestion
🎤 Q4: Difference between DNS and ARP?
DNS	ARP
Name → IP	IP → MAC
Internet level	Local network
